prompt_template:
Rank the following SKUs by stockout urgency. A SKU is urgent if days_of_cover < 3 or if daily demand exceeds current stock. For each SKU, assign a score (0-100, higher = more urgent) and provide a brief reason.

Candidates:
{% for row in dsp_data %}
- {{ row.sku }} ({{ row.category }}): {{ row.days_of_cover }} days of cover, {{ row.projected_daily_demand }} daily demand
{% endfor %}

Return a JSON array of items, each with: id (sku), rank (1-10), score (0-100), reason (text).
